= Sinatra::Fedora

A Sinatra (http://github.com/sinatra/sinatra) class that provides the ability to automatically map controllers into the URL. Acts like a very light "wrapper" around Sinatra::Base.

tl;dr A classier way for Sinatra

== Usage

Just browse through the source to see an incredibly easy layout.

== Contributors

* Jonathan Stott (https://github.com/namelessjon) <-- Pretty much wrote the entire thing.